fields.title: Wagtail
fields.content: A fresh take on content management. Elegant. Open source. Easy.

fields.title: Cookiecutter
fields.content: A command-line utility that creates projects from cookiecutters (project templates). E.g. Python package projects, jQuery plugin projects.

fields.title: Foundation
fields.content: The most advanced responsive front-end framework in the world.

fields.body: A cookiecutter template for Wagtail CMS featuring Zurb Foundation front-end framework.
